   u add loop so the song be repeated by itself
   u add preload so the song loads it self before u click at it as same as it happnes on youtube and u write auto means
   if speed of the internet is low the song wont be loaded by it self nd if the internet is ok
   it gonna loadednone mean no autoload
   meatadata means autuload

